e plans to raise $750M via ECBs, dollar bonds for growth.\nTalks ongoing with investors, banks from Singapore, Taiwan per MD Nirmal Jain.","summary":"IIFL Finance plans to raise $750M via ECBs, dollar bonds for growth.\nTalks ongoing with investors, banks from Singapore, Taiwan per MD Nirmal Jain.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/banking/finance/iifl-finance-to-raise-up-to-750-million-via-ecbs-dollar-bonds/articleshow/128792394.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-26T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"814053559358605056","title":"IIFL Finance approves issuance of 1,00,000 NCDs via private placement, totaling up to ₹1,000 crore.\nNCDs to be listed on NSE; rated with 2% p.a. interest for delayed payments beyond 3 months.","summary":"IIFL Finance approves issuance of 1,00,000 NCDs via private placement, totaling up to ₹1,000 crore.\nNCDs to be listed on NSE; rated with 2% p.a. interest for delayed payments beyond 3 months.","url":"https://sqst.in/gvgDz","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-24T14:08:12","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"504595","title":"IIFL Finance to review terms for its NCD issuance on February 24.","summary":"IIFL Finance to review terms for its NCD issuance on February 24.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T19:05:22","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"504591","title":"IIFL Finance Ltd announces a board meeting on Feb 24, 2026, to discuss issuance of non-convertible debentures.\nThe proposed private placement aims to raise funds up to Rs. 10,000 crore as per earlier intimation from May 2025.","summary":"IIFL Finance Ltd announces a board meeting on Feb 24, 2026, to discuss issuance of non-convertible debentures.\nThe proposed private placement aims to raise funds up to Rs. 10,000 crore as per earlier intimation from May 2025.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=ed894f99-0e97-414f-ae33-f340a88809c7.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T18:57:28","source":"BSE"},{"id":"500893","t